          "message": "=Hi {{ $('Pick First Free').item.json.name }}, your {{ $('Pick First Free').item.json.service }} is booked for {{ DateTime.fromISO($('Pick First Free').item.json.startTime).toFormat('MMM d, h:mm a') }} with {{ $('Pick First Free').item.json.stylistName }}. See you then!",
